       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. COBOL-SQLITE-TEST-CALLBACK.
       DATA DIVISION.
       LINKAGE SECTION.
           77 PTR              POINTER.
           77 NUM-COLUMNS      PIC S9(09).
           01 COL-VALUES.
               02 ID-COLUMN    POINTER.
               02 NAME-COLUMN  POINTER.
           77 COL-NAME         POINTER.
           77 WS-ID-COLUMN     PIC 99.
           77 WS-NAME-COLUMN   PIC X(30).
